青年歐聯，表現亮眼已經引起關注；今季由U19￼上二隊，20場入6球7助攻，其盤扭能力更加令人驚喜。<br />\n<br />\n今季其實佢已經最歐聯分組賽後備上陣過，當時係對俄羅斯的辛尼特￼￼<br />\n<br />\n依家多蒙特好似有好多多面的攻擊球員，但真係拉到邊的翼鋒球員￼其實係得Sancho 同因傷患導致狀態起起伏伏的Thorgan Hazard。Brandt, ￼Reus, Reyna 好似更加適合在中路發展，始終依家提速係差啲<br />\n<br />\n最大問題係即使Guerreiro 傷愈，佢好多時都係入中間/偏左幫助串連；<br />\n右邊Muenier 垃圾，幫唔到進攻（固然防守都幫唔到）￼已經唔需要再多講。￼￼<br />\n<br />\n兩閘拉唔闊，兩翼如果冇Sancho 靠世三細佬就大鑊。<br />\n<br />\n拉闊球場的闊度，以前有Hakimi 同Sancho 都仲有得傾。￼以家唯有睇吓Knauff 可唔可以把握機會，始終可以打到右閘或者右翼￼，都係一個優勢￼。始終呢兩個位置都要人￼<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n又J幻幻"},{"pid":"bb10c83e5aa3382fc2ce29e7d6b6c314741eb2f1","tid":2454973,"uid":12169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-21T14:39:14.000Z","msg":"點睇我Durm騎撚住你垃圾多牙"},{"pid":"a3af25b06f7c39714ba8fc6a32da9deaf69de177","tid":2454973,"uid":11501,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bb10c83e5aa3382fc2ce29e7d6b6c314741eb2f1","tid":2454973,"uid":12169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-21T14:39:14.000Z","msg":"點睇我Durm騎撚住你垃圾多牙"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-21T14:40:21.000Z","msg":"仲有rode"},{"pid":"c79d005343081cbf222d65ceaf502c8091fac47d","tid":2454973,"uid":62296,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-21T15:07:36.000Z","msg":"Peter又想救我多<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0a72786b369e559a20dc9469e4ee125be057670","tid":2454973,"uid":12169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-21T15:09:45.000Z","msg":"Peter 0:3<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e58a4092ad41e4ebcd07b5ad5cb12c6237bca30","tid":2454973,"uid":99978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b0a72786b369e559a20dc9469e4ee125be057670","tid":2454973,"uid":12169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-21T15:09:45.000Z","msg":"Peter 0:3<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-21T19:01:05.000Z","msg":"Peter不嬲關鍵時刻就幫到盡"},{"pid":"81e30b00c8c49a131